*{{rhymes|ɜː(r)fɪt}}

===Noun===
{{en-noun|-}}

# An [[excessive]] [[amount]] of something.
#* ''A '''surfeit''' of wheat is driving down the price.''
# [[overindulgence|Overindulgence]] in either [[food]] or [[drink]]; [[overeat]]ing.
# A [[sickness]] or condition caused by overindulgence.
#* ''King Henry I is said to have died of a '''surfeit''' of [[lamprey]]s.''

