{{seeCites}}

====Synonyms====
*{{italbrac|excessive amount of something}}: [[excess]], [[glut]], [[overabundance]], [[superfluity]], [[surplus]]
*{{italbrac|overindulgence in food or drink}}: [[gluttony]], [[overeating]], [[overindulgence]]

===Verb===
{{en-verb}}

# {{transitive}} To [[fill]] to excess.
# {{transitive}} To [[feed]] someone to excess.
#: ''She '''surfeited''' her children on sweets.''
# {{context|intransitive|reflexive}} To [[overeat]] or [[feed]] to excess.
# {{context|intransitive|reflexive}} To [[sicken]] from overindulgence.

